begin the grimoire.

conjure ritual named factorial with n to begin:
    if the signs show n less than 2 then return 1.
    return n multiplied by through ritual factorial with n lesser by 1.
end ritual.

inscribe whispers of "Factorials (recursive):".
summon the idx with essence of 1.
repeat the incantation 10 times to begin:
    inscribe idx bound with whispers of "! = " bound with through ritual factorial with idx.
    enchant idx with idx greater by 1.
end loop.

close the grimoire.
